research_municipality_step.notes: The elected officials for Surfside Beach City, TX, include the Mayor, Mayor Pro Tem, and four other Council Members (referred to as Alderpersons/Aldermen in some sources). The designations for specific wards or districts were not specified in the search results, so they are listed as empty arrays. Information regarding Mayor Gregg Bisso in a July 2024 YouTube video appears to be outdated or refer to a different context, as the official city website and Texas Municipal League directory list Zack Parsch as the current Mayor.
